# API integrations package (`src/api`)

When adding any 3rd-party integration (Gemini, Stripe, Email providers, analytics, etc.):

- **Create a folder under** `src/api/<provider>/`
- **Keep HTTP clients and SDK usage inside** `src/api/**` (components/pages should not call axios/fetch directly)
- **Export a small, typed surface** from `src/api/<provider>/index.ts`
- **Keep env var reads inside** the integration package (e.g. `VITE_*` access in `src/api/**`)
- **Prefer explicit, typed functions** over generic wrappers

## Example layout

```text
src/api/
  gemini/
    client.ts
    types.ts
    index.ts
```

